9-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134":1.0},"text":"Hinton is best known for backpropagation, a technique for training neural networks that revolutionized AI research."},{"citations":{"a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134":1.0},"text":"In 2013, Google acquired Hinton\u2019s startup DNNresearch for $44 million, and he joined Google as a research scientist."},{"citations":{"a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134":1.0},"text":"Hinton\u2019s warnings highlight the need for global collaboration to ensure AI development aligns with human safety and ethics."},{"citations":{"d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079":1.0},"text":"Experts like Stuart Russell and Nick Bostrom have echoed Hinton\u2019s concerns, advocating for stricter oversight of AI advancements."},{"citations":{"a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134":1.0},"text":"The public should recognize that AI\u2019s rapid growth requires careful management to mitigate risks while harnessing its benefits."},{"citations":{"a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134":1.0},"text":"Hinton\u2019s resignation underscores the urgency of addressing AI\u2019s potential to disrupt jobs, privacy, and global security."},{"citations":{"a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134":1.0},"text":"The debate over AI\u2019s future reflects broader tensions between innovation and responsibility in technology."},{"citations":{"a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134":1.0},"text":"Hinton\u2019s legacy emphasizes the importance of ethical considerations in shaping AI\u2019s trajectory."},{"citations":{"a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134":1.0},"text":"The call for caution in AI development highlights the need for transparency, accountability, and public engagement."},{"citations":{"a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134":1.0},"text":"As AI continues to evolve, balancing its potential with its risks will be critical for ensuring a safer future."}],"answer":[{"citations":{},"te