mber 16. There are four limited Christmas gifts, including\u201c LABUBU Christmas Jelly Sticks \u201d for every purchase, \u201cSKULLPANDA Christmas Card \u201d for every purchase.\" Christmas gift bag \"and\" Christmas transparent hanging ball \"for spending over $1299.\n# LABUBU Diver Lift Card # NANTEX Mall # Limited # POPMART # Christmas","metadata":{"content_type":"text/html","provenance":"cc-news_2022-0036.json.gz:4542","uncompressed_offset":641584784,"url":"www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20221202004638-260405","warc_date":"2022-12-02T15:02:19.000Z","warc_filename":"<urn:uuid:e28eb68f-8751-4971-92ce-84a78c57f3d3>","warc_url":"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20221202004638-260405"},"created":"2022-12-02T15:26:29.000Z","lang":"eng"}}}
