or the new akim of Aktobe region\nThe archive that filmmakers have been waiting for\nHeavy rains flooded Las Vegas\nTokayev appointed the head of the new Ministry of Industry and Construction\nShandong is the third trade regional partner of Kazakhstan in China\nCreativity is now at a price.\nImpostor Trash\nTens of thousands of people are stuck at the festival in the United States because of the rains\nTyphoon Haikui is approaching Taiwan\nBusinessmen want to pay for water as pensioners\nFair within Days of Culture of Tajikistan in Kazakhstan to be held in Astana\nMinister of Education of the Republic of Kazakhstan spoke about wearing the hijab in schools\nKazakhstanis will be able to transfer license plates to the new owner online\nMuza Kayuma Mukhamedkhanova\n\"Golden mine\" in the vicinity of Maralda\nHow to learn a language and make friends\nPresidents Tokayev and Rahmon visited the Main Mosque of Astana\nDinmukhamed Kunaev: I believe in my people, their future is bright\nWhere to watch live the fight Kosobutsky - Adjagba\nA foreigner who was on the run for 15 years was detained in Astana\nThe fire at the mine \"Kazakhstan\": what kind of help will the affected miners receive\nRescuers found a tourist missing in the mountains of Kok-Zhailau\nBehind the wheel of a service car and without a license removed a relative of a police chief in Shymkent\nResidents of Semey demand to cancel the entrance fee to the cemetery\nTajik citizens arrested in Almaty for robbery\nIn Semey, the memory of the victims of nuclear tests was honored\nDead girl found mushroom pickers in Kostanay region\nDouble murder in Arys: detained the alleged customer and executors\n5-year-old niece beaten by girl in Astana \u2013 reaction of police and children \u2019 s ombudsman\nA military driver saved a teenage girl from suicide in Astana\nRead also\nPricing in life\nI swear I will burn my tongue!\nAnother palace.\nIcebreaker\nDo not deprive the living space\nArchive\n\u2022 [[year]]\n\u2022 [[mon